author: Chris Elliott
title: St. Thomas football team takes on school from Toronto
text:
St. Thomas football team takes on school from Toronto Chris Elliott Published 5:08 pm, Sunday, October 11, 2015 
St. Thomas High School hosted St. Michael's College School, a team from the Toronto area, during Week 7. 
The Eagles dominated their visitors from north of the border, but displayed good sportsmanship until the end. Photo: Chris Elliott / For The Chronicle Image 1 of / 1
